snippet.title: Henchman Story - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Henchman Story is available on PC, Switch, PS4, PS5, Xbox One and Xbox Series X/S on 10/14:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1449510/Henchman_Story/

Play as a beleaguered henchman working for a bumbling supervillain in an interactive slice of superhero satire filled with colorful characters and a branching storyline. Because even henchmen have bills to pay, but sometimes, even henchmen can make choices that change everything.

Console versions published by Top Hat Studios, Inc
© Silken Sail Entertainment, 2021
